    "title": "You definitely don\u2019t want to miss this jaw-dropping interview of Assam Chief Min...",
    "description": "You definitely don\u2019t want to miss this jaw-dropping interview of Assam Chief Minister Himanta Biswa Sarma with ABP Live . When asked whether undocumented individuals suspected to be of Bangladeshi origin are handed over to Bangladesh through proper channels, the Bharatiya Janata Party (BJP) leader from the northern region and Chief Minister Sarma said it\u2019s difficult to go through India\u2019s Ministry of External Affairs. So, they wait until nightfall and push them back under the cover of darkness, when no border guard personnel are present. What\u2019s surprising is that the Chief Minister seems completely unaware that it\u2019s been 15 years since the Bangladesh Rifles were renamed the Border Guard Bangladesh or BGB and there's in-fact an extradition treaty between India and Bangladesh. Footage courtesy of ABP News",
